            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once everything has been in the oven for 25 mins, add the<strong> green beans</strong> to a pot, cover them with <strong>boiled water</strong> (just enough to cover them) with a pinch of <strong>salt</strong></p>\n<p>Bring to the boil over a high heat and cook for 3-4 min or until tender</p>\n<p>Once done, drain</p>",
